üìä Key Analysis Highlights / Resultados Clave
Top global platforms: PS2, Xbox 360, PS3, Wii, DS, with regional differences.

Most sold genres in NA and EU: Action, Shooter, Sports; in Japan: Role-Playing.

ESRB E (Everyone) rating dominates sales in NA and EU.

Weak correlation between critic/user scores and sales; critic scores slightly more influential.

Statistical tests show significant difference in user ratings between Xbox One and PC, but not between Action and Sports genres.

Principales plataformas globales: PS2, Xbox 360, PS3, Wii, DS, con diferencias regionales.

G√©neros m√°s vendidos en NA y EU: Action, Shooter, Sports; en Jap√≥n: Role-Playing.

Clasificaci√≥n ESRB E (Everyone) domina ventas en NA y EU.

Correlaci√≥n d√©bil entre valoraciones y ventas, con mayor influencia de las cr√≠ticas.

Pruebas estad√≠sticas indican diferencia significativa en valoraciones entre Xbox One y PC, pero no entre g√©neros Action y Sports.

